{"type":"message","id":"a2da394c","parentId":"cb39db86","timestamp":"2026-03-23T21:41:31.220Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_z57engyadglz_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5559\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=4072\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] tic/classifier.py\r\n[mutation proposed] tic/classifier.py\r\n[master 16bbdf9] pulse: 2026-03-23 174102\n 7 files changed, 381 insertions(+), 131 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 174102.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 174102.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 172102.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 174102 - The TIC experiment requires a classifier that can distinguish invariant (causally significant) vs variant content across pulse logs. A Python script processing the existing pulse_*.md files is the most direct path to validating the Compression-Causal Duality hypothesis.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"mild-glade","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5559\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=4072\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] tic/classifier.py\r\n[mutation proposed] tic/classifier.py\r\n[master 16bbdf9] pulse: 2026-03-23 174102\n 7 files changed, 381 insertions(+), 131 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-23 174102.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-23 174102.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-23 172102.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-23 174102 - The TIC experiment requires a classifier that can distinguish invariant (causally significant) vs variant content across pulse logs. A Python script processing the existing pulse_*.md files is the most direct path to validating the Compression-Causal Duality hypothesis.\r\n","name":"& C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\